column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift, err_u, err_g, err_r, err_i, err_z, extinction_u, extinction_g, extinction_r, extinction_i, extinction_z, deVRad_u, deVRad_g, deVRad_r, deVRad_i, deVRad_z FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE s.class = galaxy#
